speaker: C
text: And I did say yes on the chocolate, but again, you ride it only 20 miles, so what do you think?

speaker: R
text: I think no, I mean, there's some energy in the chocolate, but in the butter it would probably be more energy efficient. It just doesn't make enough of a difference, I don't think. People will be able to use their bodily reserves to go for a couple of days without having to eat. Just an extra thing to carry.
